{
  "info": {
    "name": "ChainBois API - Phase 1 (Auth + Game + Leaderboard)",
    "description": "Phase 1 endpoints: Auth, Game, Leaderboard, Health & Settings.\n\nThe `base_url` is pre-set to the live testnet API at https://test-2.ghettopigeon.com/api/v1.\nSet the `firebase_token` variable after signing in via Firebase Auth.\n\nThe `test_address` is pre-set to the nft_store wallet which holds 50 ChainBoi NFTs on Fuji testnet.\n\n## How to Import\n1. Open Postman (desktop app or web)\n2. Click **Import** (top-left)\n3. Drag and drop this JSON file, or click **Upload Files** and select it\n4. The collection appears in the sidebar under **Collections**\n5. Click the collection name, then the **Variables** tab to review/set variables\n6. Set `firebase_token` (get via Firebase Auth SDK: `user.getIdToken()`)\n7. Optionally set `test_uid` (get from /auth/create-user response)\n\n## Snowtrace Explorer (Fuji Testnet)\n- BattleToken: https://testnet.snowtrace.io/address/0xcC704c908A37A78d944a8310F8ebc0c0456CbeC0\n- ChainBoisNFT: https://testnet.snowtrace.io/address/0xB2FDDb56D85073BCBE245D46dbC1BE4D4541305b\n- WeaponNFT: https://testnet.snowtrace.io/address/0xa2AFf3105668124A187b1212Ab850bf8b98dD07d\n- NFT Store Wallet: https://testnet.snowtrace.io/address/0x469622d0FB5ED43B2e7C45E98D355F2cf03816a0\n- Weapon Store: https://testnet.snowtrace.io/address/0xD40e6631617B7557C28789bAc01648A74753739C\n- Prize Pool: https://testnet.snowtrace.io/address/0xc81F02E4bbA2F891E5D831f2dDDD9eDD61F3F92e",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "https://test-2.ghettopigeon.com/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "firebase_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "test_address",
      "value": "0x469622d0FB5ED43B2e7C45E98D355F2cf03816a0",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "test_uid",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Check User Exists",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/check-user/testuser@chainbois.com",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "check-user", "testuser@chainbois.com"]
            },
            "description": "Check if a user with the given email exists in Firebase Auth.\n\nNo auth required. Replace the email in the URL path.\nReturns { exists: true/false }."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "User Exists",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"exists\": true\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "User Not Found",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"exists\": false\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Invalid Email",
              "status": "Bad Request",
              "code": 400,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Please provide a valid email address\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Create User",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"testuser@chainbois.com\",\n  \"password\": \"testpassword123\",\n  \"username\": \"TestPlayer1\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/create-user",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "create-user"]
            },
            "description": "Create a new Firebase Auth user and write initial data to Firebase RTDB.\n\nNo auth token required.\n\nRate limit: 20 requests per 15 minutes."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success",
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"uid\": \"abc123def456\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Duplicate Email",
              "status": "Bad Request",
              "code": 400,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"error\": \"Email is already registered\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{firebase_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"address\": \"{{test_address}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login with Firebase Auth token + wallet address.\n\nLookup: address-primary, uid-fallback (for web2->web3 upgrade).\nChecks on-chain NFT ownership, syncs assets to Firebase for Unity game.\nAuto-upgrades WEB2->WEB3 when NFT detected, auto-downgrades when lost.\n\nRate limit: 20 requests per 15 minutes."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success (Web3 User with NFTs)",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"user\": {\n      \"uid\": \"abc123\",\n      \"username\": \"TestPlayer1\",\n      \"address\": \"0x469622d0fb5ed43b2e7c45e98d355f2cf03816a0\",\n      \"playerType\": \"web3\",\n      \"pointsBalance\": 0,\n      \"level\": 0,\n      \"score\": 0,\n      \"highScore\": 0,\n      \"gamesPlayed\": 0,\n      \"hasNft\": true,\n      \"nftTokenId\": 1,\n      \"isBanned\": false,\n      \"hasClaimed\": false,\n      \"lastLogin\": \"2026-03-04T21:55:00.000Z\"\n    },\n    \"assets\": [{ \"tokenId\": 1, \"level\": 0 }],\n    \"weapons\": []\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Success (Web2 User, no NFTs)",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"user\": {\n      \"uid\": \"abc123\",\n      \"username\": \"TestPlayer1\",\n      \"address\": \"0x80dbc4c3c17eb35160aeec41b1590d5f028079c0\",\n      \"playerType\": \"web2\",\n      \"pointsBalance\": 0,\n      \"level\": 0,\n      \"score\": 0,\n      \"highScore\": 0,\n      \"gamesPlayed\": 0,\n      \"hasNft\": false,\n      \"nftTokenId\": null,\n      \"isBanned\": false,\n      \"hasClaimed\": false,\n      \"lastLogin\": \"2026-03-04T21:55:00.000Z\"\n    },\n    \"assets\": [],\n    \"weapons\": []\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Current User",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{firebase_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/me",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Get the authenticated user's profile.\n\nReturns user data from MongoDB (no blockchain call)."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"user\": {\n      \"uid\": \"abc123\",\n      \"username\": \"TestPlayer1\",\n      \"address\": \"0x469622d0fb5ed43b2e7c45e98d355f2cf03816a0\",\n      \"playerType\": \"web3\",\n      \"pointsBalance\": 0,\n      \"level\": 0,\n      \"score\": 0,\n      \"highScore\": 0,\n      \"gamesPlayed\": 0,\n      \"hasNft\": true,\n      \"nftTokenId\": 1,\n      \"isBanned\": false,\n      \"hasClaimed\": false,\n      \"lastLogin\": \"2026-03-04T21:55:00.000Z\"\n    }\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{firebase_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "Logout: revokes Firebase refresh tokens and clears game data in Firebase RTDB.\n\nAfter logout, Firebase RTDB is set to: hasNFT=false, level=0, weapons=null."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Logged out successfully\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Game",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Verify Assets",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{firebase_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/game/verify-assets",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["game", "verify-assets"]
            },
            "description": "Re-fetch NFT ownership from on-chain and update MongoDB + Firebase.\n\nUse this to refresh asset data without re-logging in."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success (has NFTs)",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"hasNft\": true,\n    \"assets\": [{ \"tokenId\": 1, \"level\": 0 }],\n    \"ownedWeaponNfts\": []\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Success (no NFTs)",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"hasNft\": false,\n    \"assets\": [],\n    \"ownedWeaponNfts\": []\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Set Avatar",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{firebase_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"tokenId\": 1\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/game/set-avatar",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["game", "set-avatar"]
            },
            "description": "Set the user's active ChainBoi NFT (CB).\n\nVerifies on-chain that the user owns the specified tokenId.\nTokens #1-50 exist on Fuji testnet (owned by nft_store wallet)."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"tokenId\": 1,\n    \"level\": 0\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Unowned Token",
              "status": "Bad Request",
              "code": 400,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"error\": \"Failed to verify NFT ownership. Token may not exist.\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Download Game (Win)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/game/download/win",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["game", "download", "win"]
            },
            "description": "Download the Windows game build.\n\nNo auth required. Streams the zip file.\nCurrently returns 404 (game file not uploaded yet)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Download Game (APK)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/game/download/apk",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["game", "download", "apk"]
            },
            "description": "Download the Android APK.\n\nNo auth required. Streams the APK file.\nCurrently returns 404 (game file not uploaded yet)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Game Info",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/game/info",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["game", "info"]
            },
            "description": "Get game download count, trailer URL, and platform availability.\n\nNo auth required."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"downloads\": 0,\n    \"trailer\": \"\",\n    \"platforms\": {\n      \"win\": false,\n      \"apk\": false\n    }\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Leaderboard",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Leaderboard (All-Time)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/leaderboard",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["leaderboard"]
            },
            "description": "Get the overall leaderboard (all-time scores).\n\nNo auth required.\nQuery params: limit (default 100, max 500), page (default 1)."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"period\": \"all\",\n  \"startDate\": null,\n  \"endDate\": null,\n  \"currentPage\": 1,\n  \"totalPages\": 1,\n  \"totalUsers\": 2,\n  \"leaderboard\": [\n    { \"uid\": \"abc123\", \"username\": \"Player1\", \"scoreGained\": 5000, \"currentScore\": 5000, \"rank\": 1 }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Leaderboard by Period (24 Hours)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/leaderboard/24hours",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["leaderboard", "24hours"]
            },
            "description": "Get leaderboard for the last 24 hours.\n\nNo auth required.\nValid periods: 30min, 1hour, 24hours, 2days, week, month, year, all."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"period\": \"24hours\",\n  \"startDate\": \"2026-03-03T12:00:00.000Z\",\n  \"endDate\": \"2026-03-04T12:00:00.000Z\",\n  \"currentPage\": 1,\n  \"totalPages\": 1,\n  \"totalUsers\": 0,\n  \"leaderboard\": []\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Leaderboard by Period (Week)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/leaderboard/week",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["leaderboard", "week"]
            },
            "description": "Get the weekly leaderboard.\n\nNo auth required.\nSupports custom date ranges via startDate/endDate query params (ISO 8601)."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"period\": \"week\",\n  \"startDate\": \"2026-02-25T00:00:00.000Z\",\n  \"endDate\": \"2026-03-04T00:00:00.000Z\",\n  \"currentPage\": 1,\n  \"totalPages\": 1,\n  \"totalUsers\": 0,\n  \"leaderboard\": []\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Leaderboard with Pagination",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/leaderboard?limit=5&page=1",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["leaderboard"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "limit", "value": "5" },
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get leaderboard with custom page size.\n\nlimit: 1-500 (default 100)\npage: 1-indexed (default 1)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User Rank (All-Time)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{firebase_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/leaderboard/rank/{{test_uid}}?period=all",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["leaderboard", "rank", "{{test_uid}}"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "period", "value": "all" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get a specific user's rank on the leaderboard.\n\nRequires auth. Set test_uid variable.\nQuery param: period (default 'all').\nValid periods: 30min, 1hour, 24hours, 2days, week, month, year, all."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"uid\": \"abc123\",\n  \"period\": \"all\",\n  \"rank\": 1,\n  \"scoreGained\": 0,\n  \"currentScore\": 0\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User Rank (Weekly)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{firebase_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/leaderboard/rank/{{test_uid}}?period=week",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["leaderboard", "rank", "{{test_uid}}"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "period", "value": "week" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get a specific user's weekly rank.\n\nRequires auth."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"uid\": \"abc123\",\n  \"period\": \"week\",\n  \"rank\": 1,\n  \"scoreGained\": 0,\n  \"currentScore\": 0\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Health & Settings",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Settings",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/settings",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["settings"]
            },
            "description": "Get public game settings (costs, thresholds, etc.).\n\nNo auth required. The contracts field is excluded for security."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"tournamentSchedule\": { \"startDay\": 3, \"startHour\": 12, \"durationHours\": 120, \"cooldownHours\": 48 },\n    \"prizePools\": { \"1\": 2, \"2\": 4, \"3\": 6, \"4\": 8, \"5\": 10, \"6\": 12, \"7\": 14 },\n    \"levelUpCosts\": { \"1\": 1, \"2\": 1, \"3\": 2, \"4\": 2, \"5\": 3, \"6\": 3, \"7\": 5 },\n    \"battleTokenDecimals\": 18,\n    \"maxPointsPerMatch\": 5000,\n    \"burnRate\": 0.5,\n    \"teamRevenueSplit\": 0.25,\n    \"awardPoolSplit\": 0.75,\n    \"armoryClosedDuringCooldown\": true,\n    \"claimLimit\": 1,\n    \"claimEnabled\": true,\n    \"downloads\": 0,\n    \"trailer\": null\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            },
            "description": "Check API and MongoDB status.\n\nReturns 200 if healthy, 503 if MongoDB disconnected."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Healthy",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"status\": \"ok\",\n    \"uptime\": 432,\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-04T21:55:07.637Z\",\n    \"services\": {\n      \"mongodb\": \"connected\"\n    }\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
